fields.content: Beauty4U is Ireland's #1 Source for Hair and Beauty services and products. We offer premium hair and beauty services at affordable prices. Since opening in 2020, we have continued to expand across the country. We hope to see you in a salon near you!

fields.name: Alfaparf Semi Di Lino Curls
fields.description: Hydrates curls making hair soft tangle free and frizz free. Suitable for fine to medium curly hair.

fields.name: Dermalogica Skin Smoothing 2.0
fields.description: Next-generation moisturiser with Active HydraMesh Technology™ infuses skin with 48 hours of continuous hydration and helps protect against environmental stress. This best-selling moisturiser features a state-of-the-art complex that works on a molecular level to help reduce Trans-Epidermal Water Loss (TEWL) and infuse skin with 48 hours of vital moisture. This advanced technology also helps shield skin’s natural microbiome from environmental stress. A dynamic Hyaluronic Acid Complex with Mallow, Cucumber and Arnica distributes hydration throughout the skin, helping to lock in moisture for lasting hydration. Also formulated with naturally-antioxidant Grape Seed Extract, Vitamin C and Vitamin E.

fields.name: Dermalogica Special Cleansing Gel
fields.description: Dermalogica Special Cleansing Gel foams away impurities without leaving your skin feeling tight or dry. Anti-inflammatory balm mint and lavender extracts soothe your skin, while natural quillaja saponaria gently foams away toxins and cleanses debris. Fragrance and soap free, Dermalogica Special Cleansing Gel is ideal for combination to normal skin. Designed to thoroughly remove impurities without disturbing the skin’s natural moisture balance, this cleanser will leave your skin feeling cool and calm.

fields.name: Jane Iredale PurePressed Base Mineral Foundation Refill
fields.description: A foundation and concealer in one which offers broad spectrum UV protection, the luxurious formula is enriched with antioxidant pine bark and pomegranate extracts that combat free radicals and minimise UV damage.

fields.name: Jane Iredale Liquid Minerals Foundation
fields.description: A gorgeous foundation and treatment serum in one, Jane Iredale Liquid Minerals Foundation will totally transform your look. Boasting a special liquid formulation, this foundation plumps and hydrates your skin while providing sheer to medium coverage. Also minimising lines, wrinkles and pores, it creates a wonderfully flawless complexion. The soothing feel calms any inflammation and the actives will gain the time they need to penetrate your skin courtesy of the latest liposome technology. Have you ever benefitted from a foundation that can do so much and so effortlessly?

fields.name: Joico HydraSplash Hydrating Shampoo 300ml
fields.description:
Suitable for fine/medium dry hair

Joico HydraSplash gently cleanses away residue without taking essential natural moisture from the hair, leaving your dry hair nourished soft, and healthy looking, without being weighed down.

How to use:

Apply to wet hair.
Lather.
Rinse well, repeat if necessary
Follow with Hydra Splash Conditioner
